title: Fan, late 19th century
medium:
Medium: cotton, silk, tortoise shell, steel
Technique: lace motifs applied to net, embroidered
description: Folding fan with a black silk net leaf with white cotton needle lace motifs of irises, scrolls and flower sprays applied; lace elements embroidered with silver sequins. The sticks are of tortoise shell, piqué, with guards ending in a serpentine form.
